  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka President declares fuel, power, health services as essential",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka President Ranil Wickremesinghe has declared fuel, electricity and health as essential services in a gazette notice using powers available when they were though \u2018likely to be impeded\u2019.",
        "The order will apply to any government agency, corporation, local body, co-operative societies or their branches from September 03.",
        "The order was issued under powers allowing them to be made essential if such services \u201clikely to be impeded or interrupted.\u201d",
        "The order comes shortly after ex-President Gotabaya Rajapaksa returned to the island.",
        "Sri Lanka is now grappling with the worst currency crises in the history of the island\u2019s central bank. (Colombo/Sept04/2022)"
      ],
